## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and may not fully capture the most recent shifts in public opinion or legislative changes. Additionally, the sources reflect a range of perspectives, but there may be other viewpoints not covered in this report. The complexity of the issue means that individual opinions can vary widely based on personal experiences and regional differences.